org.matsim.contrib.minibus.operator

Class CarefulMultiPlanOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.minibus.operator.CarefulMultiPlanOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operator

    public final class CarefulMultiPlanOperator
extends Object
    This operator has multiple plans. Each is weighted by the number of vehicles associated with. The number of vehicles depends on the score per vehicle and plan. In the end, each plan should have approximately the same score. In contrast to MultiPlanOperator, this operator accepts all plans as blueprints for replanning, again picking one is a weighted random draw. Vehicle are shifted away from plans instantly, i.e. if a plan scored negative at least one vehicle is removed. Vehicles are distributed to positive plans and new plans.
    Author:
    aneumann
